## Function Parameters

- Use default parameter values for optional parameters:
  ```typescript
  function processData(data: string, options: Options = {}) {
    // ...
  }
  ```
- Use destructuring with defaults for object parameters:
  ```typescript
  function processConfig({ 
    maxRetries = 3, 
    timeout = 1000 
  }: Partial<Config> = {}) {
    // ...
  }